# Unity Scene Files
# =================
# This folder contains Unity scene files for the game.
#
# Available Scenes:
# -----------------
# - MainMenu.unity - Main menu scene template (requires Unity Editor setup)
# - MainGame.unity - Main gameplay scene (to be created in Unity Editor)
#
# MainMenu Scene Setup (Required Steps in Unity Editor):
# -------------------------------------------------------
# After opening this project in Unity, complete the following setup:
#
# 1. Add GameManager Component:
#    - Select the "Managers" GameObject in the hierarchy
#    - Add Component -> Scripts -> GameManager
#
# 2. Configure MainMenuCanvas:
#    - Add CanvasScaler component (UI Scale Mode: Scale With Screen Size)
#    - Add GraphicRaycaster component
#
# 3. Setup TitleText:
#    - Add TextMeshPro - Text component
#    - Set Text to "Jacameno: Adult Life"
#    - Configure font size and alignment
#
# 4. Setup StartButton:
#    - Add Image component (for button background)
#    - Add Button component
#    - Add child object with TextMeshPro text "Start Game"
#
# 5. Setup QuitButton:
#    - Add Image component (for button background)
#    - Add Button component
#    - Add child object with TextMeshPro text "Quit"
#
# 6. Create MainMenuManager GameObject:
#    - Add MainMenuUI script component
#    - Assign startGameButton and quitButton references
#
# 7. Configure EventSystem:
#    - Add EventSystem component
#    - Add StandaloneInputModule or Input System UI Input Module
#
# 8. Add Scene to Build Settings:
#    - File > Build Settings
#    - Add MainMenu scene (index 0) and MainGame scene (index 1)
